      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIGHT PATH (4) has a solid record despite not breaking through for a win in six starts. Finished in the minors last start but did run very good time (22.49). Sure to be about the mark. PAW PEARL (8) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 390m behind Starlet Bale (22.78) in a Bottom Up - Maiden. Has ability and can atone. PAW ZILLIE (1) flew the lids from out wide with a slick early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (22.65) over 390m at this track. Should be about the money. INGA RYDER (7) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
